上传制品版本到主节点不消耗流量，跨地域同步的每个节点都需要消耗一次流量。即: 制: Uploading the package version to the primary node does not consume traffic, but each node that synchronizes across regions consumes traffic once. That is: artifact version size × Number of synchronized nodes
删除整个制品或单个制品版本不消耗流量: Deleting an entire package or a single package version does not consume traffic
